<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>World News Today: Read the latest world news headlines, Current International breaking news world wide. In depth analysis and top news headlines world wide.</description><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>2026-05-31T13:51:00+05:30</lastBuildDate><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" rel="self" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/296589292.cms"/><copyright>Copyright:(C) Sun, 31 May 2026 13:51:00 IST Bennett Coleman &amp; Co. Ltd, http://in.indiatimes.com/policyterms/1554651.cms</copyright><docs>http://syndication.indiatimes.com/</docs><image><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><url>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/507610.cms</url><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link></image><item><title><![CDATA[Ukraine receives new German IRIS-T air defence launcher amid continued Russian attacks]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131420413.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Ukraine has received a new IRIS-T air defence launcher from Germany, bolstering its defenses against Russian missile and drone strikes. This latest delivery adds to previous transfers of the German-made medium-range surface-to-air missile system, which is crucial for protecting cities and infrastructure.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/defence/international/ukraine-receives-new-german-iris-t-air-defence-launcher-amid-continued-russian-missile-and-drone-attacks/articleshow/131420413.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/defence/international/ukraine-receives-new-german-iris-t-air-defence-launcher-amid-continued-russian-missile-and-drone-attacks/articleshow/131420413.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T13:34:37+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131420455,imgsize-59146.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Russia's 'fire-and-forget' $500 Yolka drone hunter that fits in soldier's hand]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131419863.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[New footage shows Russian forces deploying the "Yolka" interceptor drone system in combat, a low-cost weapon designed to counter enemy reconnaissance and FPV drones. This handheld system launches a drone that autonomously tracks and engages targets via kinetic impact, offering a portable and cost-effective solution against battlefield UAVs.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/defence/international/watch-russias-fire-and-forget-500-yolka-drone-hunter-that-fits-in-soldiers-hand/articleshow/131419863.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/defence/international/watch-russias-fire-and-forget-500-yolka-drone-hunter-that-fits-in-soldiers-hand/articleshow/131419863.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T12:45:37+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131420023,imgsize-32804.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Water, gas &amp; power outages - Pakistan's Karachi hit by utility collapse as Eid turns into crisis]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131417754.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Karachi residents endured a grim Eid-ul-Adha marked by severe water, gas, and power outages. Families struggled to cook and preserve meat amid sweltering heat, leading to widespread protests. Despite official assurances, essential services failed, forcing many to resort to costly alternatives and endure immense hardship during the festival.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/water-gas-power-outages-pakistans-karachi-hit-by-utility-collapse-as-eid-turns-into-crisis/articleshow/131417754.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/water-gas-power-outages-pakistans-karachi-hit-by-utility-collapse-as-eid-turns-into-crisis/articleshow/131417754.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T07:29:18+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131417874,imgsize-98478.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Trump to kick off US 250th anniversary concert celebrations but without several artists who quit]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131418037.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Trump will launch the Great American State Fair next month after several artists withdrew due to political concerns. Organizers Freedom 250 announced Trump's June 24 kick-off in Washington, D.C. Trump himself suggested replacing the departed performers with a "Make America Great Again Rally" for the nation's 250th anniversary.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-to-kick-off-us-250th-anniversary-concert-celebrations-but-without-several-artists-who-quit/articleshow/131418037.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-to-kick-off-us-250th-anniversary-concert-celebrations-but-without-several-artists-who-quit/articleshow/131418037.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T08:34:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131418054,imgsize-595090.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Israel captures strategic Lebanon castle after days of fighting despite ceasefire]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131419389.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Israeli troops have captured the strategic Beaufort Castle in southern Lebanon, marking their deepest incursion in over 26 years. This territorial gain occurred despite an existing ceasefire, with forces advancing near Nabatiyeh to dismantle Hezbollah infrastructure. The operation aims to eliminate perceived threats to Israeli civilians.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-captures-strategic-lebanon-castle-after-days-of-fighting-despite-ceasefire/articleshow/131419389.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-captures-strategic-lebanon-castle-after-days-of-fighting-despite-ceasefire/articleshow/131419389.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T11:30:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131419488,imgsize-52034.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian-origin Disney manager Jugal Daterao gets 2.5-year jail term in Russia over drug case]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131419314.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[An Indian-origin Disney executive, Jugal Daterao, has received a two-and-a-half-year prison sentence in Russia for drug possession and smuggling.  Authorities found THC-infused gummy candies in his luggage at a Moscow airport. Daterao claimed the gummies were legally prescribed in the US for post-brain surgery effects, but the court rejected his defense.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/indian-origin-disney-manager-jugal-daterao-gets-2-5-year-jail-term-in-russia-over-drug-case/articleshow/131419314.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/indian-origin-disney-manager-jugal-daterao-gets-2-5-year-jail-term-in-russia-over-drug-case/articleshow/131419314.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T11:21:46+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131419403,imgsize-925820.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[China expels NYT reporter over interview with Taiwan president]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131417789.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-expels-nyt-reporter-over-interview-with-taiwan-president/articleshow/131417789.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-expels-nyt-reporter-over-interview-with-taiwan-president/articleshow/131417789.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T07:34:17+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131417796,imgsize-776113.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[AUKUS to develop unmanned undersea vehicles, Pentagon chief says]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131417777.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/aukus-to-develop-unmanned-undersea-vehicles-pentagon-chief-says/articleshow/131417777.cms]]></link><guid><![CDAT