ers and damage to vehicles and businesses. Authorities had deployed extensive security measures amid concerns of disturbances.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/psg-champions-league-celebrations-in-france-spark-clashes-416-detained-7-police-officers-injured/articleshow/131417580.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/psg-champions-league-celebrations-in-france-spark-clashes-416-detained-7-police-officers-injured/articleshow/131417580.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T06:56:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131417670,imgsize-49212.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[In outreach to Bangladesh PM, India hails his father's 1971 address]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131417417.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/in-outreach-to-bangladesh-pm-india-hails-his-fathers-1971-address/articleshow/131417417.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/in-outreach-to-bangladesh-pm-india-hails-his-fathers-1971-address/articleshow/131417417.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T04:43:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Ahsan Tasnim</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131417424,imgsize-233856.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian student drowned at Wisconsin dam as he jumped to save three friends; feet got stuck in fishing wire]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131415460.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.i