orking-for-lawrence-bishnoi/articleshow/131415143.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/i-thought-it-was-a-toy-gun-indian-man-in-canada-says-he-had-no-idea-his-friend-was-working-for-lawrence-bishnoi/articleshow/131415143.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-31T00:45:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131415205,imgsize-51986.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US says it is 'more than capable' of resume war with Iran as talks remain unresolved]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131414356.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The US warned of renewed military action against Iran if necessary, with President Trump demanding a permanent end to Tehran's nuclear ambitions. Despite ongoing diplomatic efforts and a fragile ceasefire, tensions remain high, exacerbated by disruptions in the Strait of Hormuz and continued fighting in Lebanon.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-says-it-is-more-than-capable-of-resume-war-with-iran-as-talks-remain-unresolved/articleshow/131414356.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-says-it-is-more-than-capable-of-resume-war-with-iran-as-talks-remain-unresolved/articleshow/131414356.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T23:56:02+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131414441,imgsize-849538.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who has to leave US for Green Card and who doesn't: New USCIS rule, clarification explained]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131414334.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-has-to-leave-us-for-green-card-and-who-doesnt-have-to-new-uscis-rule-clarification-explained/articleshow/131414334.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/who-has-to-leave-us-for-green-card-and-who-doesnt-have-to-new-uscis-rule-clarification-explained/articleshow/131414334.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T23:53:52+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131414353,imgsize-95004.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['We’re with you': WHO chief rushes to Congo as Ebola outbreak worsens]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131413731.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The WHO chief is urging greater international backing to combat a rapidly spreading Ebola outbreak in the DRC, highlighting delays and community mistrust as major hurdles.  He stressed the need for local cooperation and urged countries to reconsider travel bans.  The outbreak has already reached Uganda, with thousands of cases and hundreds of deaths reported.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/were-with-you-who-chief-rushes-to-congo-as-ebola-outbreak-worsens/articleshow/131413731.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/were-with-you-who-chief-rushes-to-congo-as-ebola-outbreak-worsens/articleshow/131413731.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-30T23:23:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131413853,imgsize-39112.cms"/></item></channel></rss>